    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut 2 thin slices per person from your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> and set them aside for serving</p><p>Chop the<strong> remaining tomato[es]</strong> roughly</p><p>Wash your <strong>lettuce</strong>, pat it dry with kitchen paper then remove 1 outer leaf per person and set aside until serving</p><p>Tear the <strong>remaining lettuce</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Slice your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong> into 3 <strong>slices </strong>per person</p>",
