    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top the meat-free patty[ies] with the<strong> cheese slices</strong> and cook, covered, for a further 3 min or until the cheese has melted and the patty[ies] is cooked through</p><p>Meanwhile, slice your<strong> brioche bun[s]</strong> in half and put them in the oven for 2-3 min or until warmed through</p>",
